Spider-Man turns 60 this year and the party has not stopped as we celebrate all things Spidey. This week, we tackle one of the best modern stories in recent history....Spider-Verse! Not only is the tale a love letter to all things Spider-Man but it produced some of the best Spider-Man variants ever! We discuss the comic, the animated movie, and other multiversal Spidey adventures in this super fun episode of the Major Issues Podcast!  Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

